flavor_text_entries.red:
Although small,
its venomous
barbs render this POKéMON dangerous.
The female has
smaller horns.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
Although small,
its venomous
barbs render this POKéMON dangerous.
The female has
smaller horns.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
A mild-mannered
POKéMON that does
not like to fight. Beware, its
small horns
secrete venom.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
The poison hidden
in its small horn
is extremely po­ tent. Even a tiny
scratch can have
fatal results.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
Although not very
combative, it will
torment its foes with poison spikes
if it is threat­
ened in any way.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
Small and very
docile, it pro­
tects itself with its small, poison­
ous horn when
attacked.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
NIDORAN has barbs that secrete a
powerful poison. They are thought to
have developed as protection for this small-bodied POKéMON.
When enraged, it releases a horrible
toxin from its horn.

flavor_text_entries.sword:
Females are more sensitive to smells than males.
While foraging, they’ll use their whiskers to check
wind direction and stay downwind of predators.
flavor_text_entries.shield:
It uses its hard incisor teeth to crush and eat
berries. The tip of a female Nidoran’s horn is a
bit more rounded than the tip of a male’s horn.
